# =========================
# São Rafael - .gitignore
# =========================

# --- Planilhas e Excel ---
*.xlsx
*.xls
*.xlsm
*.xlsb
*.csv

# --- PDFs (documentação extraída da planilha) ---
*.pdf

# --- OS files ---
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
.DS_Store

# --- Editor/IDE ---
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# --- Node (caso use futuramente) ---
node_modules/
package-lock.json

# --- Env / Secrets ---
.env
.env.*
*.key
*.pem

# --- Logs ---
*.log

# --- Temp ---
*.tmp
*.bak
*.orig

# --- Playbook agent (isolado, ferramenta interna de handover) ---
# Não publica nada do agente de playbook no GitHub.
#.github/playbook-agent/
#.github/agents/playbook*.agent.md
#.github/chatmodes/playbook.chatmode.md
# (mantém .github/workflows/ e demais customizações versionadas)
